<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Northstar Studio</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Premium modern website template with a polished look and smooth interactions." />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-shell">
    <header class="topbar">
      <a href="#home" class="brand">
        <span class="brand-mark"></span>
        <span class="brand-text">Northstar Studio</span>
      </a>

      <button class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Open navigation" aria-expanded="false">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>

      <nav class="nav" id="siteNav">
        <a href="#services">Services</a>
        <a href="#work">Work</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Let’s Talk</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main id="home">
      <section class="hero section">
        <div class="hero-copy reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Premium Digital Design</p>
          <h1>Modern websites that look expensive and convert like crazy.</h1>
          <p class="hero-text">
            A polished, high-end landing page template you can open immediately in the browser.
            No frameworks. No build tools. Just clean files that work.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a Project</a>
            <a href="#work" class="btn btn-secondary">See Showcase</a>
          </div>
          <div class="stats-grid">
            <article class="stat-card">
              <strong>10+</strong>
              <span>Years design language</span>
            </article>
            <article class="stat-card">
              <strong>98%</strong>
              <span>Client satisfaction feel</span>
            </article>
            <article class="stat-card">
              <strong>24/7</strong>
              <span>Premium visual presence</span>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual reveal delay-1">
          <div class="glass-panel panel-a">
            <p>Featured Launch</p>
            <h3>Luxury Brand Refresh</h3>
            <span>Elegant UI • Smooth motion • Elite positioning</span>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-panel panel-b">
            <p>Conversion Lift</p>
            <h2>+37%</h2>
            <span>Refined structure with stronger calls to action</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-orb orb-1"></div>
          <div class="hero-orb orb-2"></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="logo-strip reveal">
        <span>TRUSTED STYLE</span>
        <span>PREMIUM UX</span>
        <span>MODERN LAYOUTS</span>
        <span>FAST LOADING</span>
        <span>CLEAN CODE</span>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="services">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Services</p>
          <h2>Built to feel sharp, premium, and credible.</h2>
          <p>
            Everything here is handcrafted to give your brand a stronger first impression.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card-grid three-col">
          <article class="feature-card reveal">
            <div class="icon-box">01</div>
            <h3>Luxury Visual Direction</h3>
            <p>Clean spacing, elegant type, layered gradients, and premium visual rhythm.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card reveal delay-1">
            <div class="icon-box">02</div>
            <h3>Responsive Layouts</h3>
            <p>Looks strong on desktop, tablet, and mobile without extra setup.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card reveal delay-2">
            <div class="icon-box">03</div>
            <h3>Smooth Interaction</h3>
            <p>Subtle motion, hover polish, and scroll reveals that add a modern wow factor.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section showcase" id="work">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Selected Work</p>
          <h2>A layout that feels like a premium agency homepage.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="showcase-grid">
          <article class="showcase-card large reveal">
            <div class="showcase-content">
              <p class="tag">Flagship Website</p>
              <h3>Executive brand presence with cinematic depth.</h3>
              <p>
                High-end positioning for founders, agencies, consultants, and premium local businesses.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="showcase-card reveal delay-1">
            <div class="showcase-content">
              <p class="tag">Product Story</p>
              <h3>Minimal and bold.</h3>
              <p>Structured messaging with strong contrast and clean hierarchy.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="showcase-card reveal delay-2">
            <div class="showcase-content">
              <p class="tag">Sales Experience</p>
              <h3>Made to convert.</h3>
              <p>Sections are arranged for clarity, trust, and action.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section split-section" id="about">
        <div class="split-copy reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Why it works</p>
          <h2>It is simple enough to deploy, but polished enough to feel custom.</h2>
          <p>
            You can upload these files exactly as they are to many hosting platforms,
            or drop them into your existing site as a starting point.
          </p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Single-click browser preview</li>
            <li>No broken dependencies</li>
            <li>Separate files so you know where everything goes</li>
            <li>Easy to edit text, colors, and sections</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card reveal delay-1">
          <p class="pricing-label">Template Value</p>
          <h3>Professional landing page</h3>
          <div class="price">Ready now</div>
          <ul>
            <li>Standalone HTML</li>
            <li>Dedicated CSS file</li>
            <li>Dedicated JS file</li>
            <li>Mobile navigation included</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary full">Use This Layout</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section testimonials">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Social Proof</p>
          <h2>Premium feel without the usual setup headache.</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid three-col">
          <article class="quote-card reveal">
            <p>“This looks clean, expensive, and actually works out of the box.”</p>
            <span>— Founder</span>
          </article>
          <article class="quote-card reveal delay-1">
            <p>“Finally something I can paste into my hosting without debugging a build system.”</p>
            <span>— Small Business Owner</span>
          </article>
          <article class="quote-card reveal delay-2">
            <p>“The sections are easy to customize and the mobile version feels polished.”</p>
            <span>— Creative Consultant</span>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section contact-section" id="contact">
        <div class="section-heading reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
          <h2>Ready to launch something that looks premium?</h2>
          <p>Replace the text below with your real email, phone number, or booking link.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-box reveal delay-1">
          <div>
            <h3>Your Business Name</h3>
            <p>Email: hello@yourdomain.com</p>
            <p>Phone: (555) 555-5555</p>
            <p>Location: Your City, State</p>
          </div>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:hello@yourdomain.com">Email Now</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <p>© <span id="year"></span> Northstar Studio. Built for a premium online presence.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
